    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road with this dependable ride! This car is in fair condition and is the perfect choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle at a great value. While it shows some honest wear and tear from its journeys, it remains a solid performer that\u2019s ready for its next chapter with a new owner!",
