    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended for those looking for a project car or a source for parts. The engine has significant trouble starting and staying idle, and there is a major leak in the transmission system that will require immediate attention. Cosmetically, the car shows its age with extensive rust on the undercarriage, several large dents on the rear panels, and a worn interior with torn upholstery. It is not currently in roadworthy condition and will likely need to be towed from the premises.",
