      "description": "This distinguished vehicle offers a seamless blend of performance and sophisticated design. Meticulously maintained and showing pride of ownership, it features a robust mechanical profile and a well-appointed interior. Engineered for reliability and comfort, this automobile represents a superior acquisition for the discerning driver seeking quality and enduring value.",
      "price": 34500.0,
